    <section class="card" style="margin-top:18px;">
      <h2>Methodology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Data:</b> Q1/2019 & Q1/2020; prep in Excel (standardization, <code>ride_length_min</code>, <code>day_of_week</code>, <code>start_hour</code>, <code>month</code>).</li>
        <li><b>Cleaning:</b> remove rides &lt;1 min and &gt;24h; drop missing times.</li>
        <li><b>Analysis:</b> KPIs, weekday/hour volume, avg duration by weekday, top stations, and 2020 <code>rideable_type</code>.</li>
      </ul>
